# Overview

This code is for a notes application, designed to read and write notes.

This code was written to learn the basics of kotlin in order to prepare to make a notes application on android.

{Provide a link to your YouTube demonstration. It should be a 4-5 minute demo of the software running and a walkthrough of the code. Focus should be on sharing what you learned about the language syntax.}

[Notes app demo](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9agZ3UVsQ1M)

# Development Environment

This code was written in the intelij ide

written using kotlin and the java.io.File and FileWritter libraries

